title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - E-jets 175 - importing the flightplan
description:
In this video we will have a look at how to create a flightplan and import it in the E-jet 175 . We will use Simbrief to create the flightplan and after that have a look at how we can get it ready to be easily added to the E-jet 175.

After having a look at how to install it we will walk through the panel to see what functionalities are available.
